restlib

Class ClientPreferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.ClientPreferences
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientPreferencesWrapper

    @Immutable
public abstract class ClientPreferences
extends Object
    Client preferences that may be used by a server to perform content negotiation. Implementations must be immutable or effectively immutable.
